《'''氛围'''》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://epaper.oeeee.com/epaper/C/html/2017-07/26/content_52270.htm |title=给你一个什么理由，你会去看一部30天才能看完的电影？-南方都市报·奥一网 |accessdate=2018-08-05 |archive-date=2018-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180805143310/http://epaper.oeeee.com/epaper/C/html/2017-07/26/content_52270.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>（{{lang-sv|''Ambiancé''}}）也译《气氛》，是一部由Anders Weberg執導的[[瑞典|瑞典]][[电影|电影]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2014/07/11/ambiance-trailer|title=Video: World record-seeking 720-hour movie now has a 72-minute trailer|website=Entertainment Weekly's EW.com|access-date=2016-04-19|archive-date=2019-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190805055300/https://ew.com/article/2014/07/11/ambiance-trailer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，預計於2020年12月13日發行，该片将长达720个小时（30天），并且将在全球放映。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.dagbladet.no/2016/04/18/kultur/sverige/film/kunst/anders_weberg/43912048/|title=Svenske Anders lager 30 dager lang film - traileren er på sju timer|website=Dagbladet.no|access-date=2016-04-19|archive-date=2016-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160421101547/http://www.dagbladet.no/2016/04/18/kultur/sverige/film/kunst/anders_weberg/43912048/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/video-72-minute-trailer-released-717973|title=[VIDEO] 72-Minute Trailer Released for Longest Film Ever, 'Ambiance'|website=The Hollywood Reporter|access-date=2016-04-19|archive-date=2016-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507200721/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/video-72-minute-trailer-released-717973|dead-url=no}}</ref>一旦电影在影片上映后，Weberg表示將会销毁片源，他说“最长的电影将不存在。”<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thelongestfilm.com/|title=A M B I A N C É - a 720 hours long film by Anders Weberg|website=The Longest Film|access-date=2016-04-19|archive-date=2016-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422100025/http://www.thelongestfilm.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他还称这将是他的最后一部电影。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/stargazing_blog/2014/07/swedish_filmmaker_anders_weberg_is_working_on_720_hour_long_movie.html|title=Swedish filmmaker Anders Weberg is working on 720-hour long movie|website=Toronto Star|access-date=2016-04-19|archive-date=2017-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730070222/https://www.thestar.com/entertainment/stargazing_blog/2014/07/swedish_filmmaker_anders_weberg_is_working_on_720_hour_long_movie.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==简介==
这部电影前提部分基于从《[[第七封印|第七封印]]》的国际象棋比赛现场，将通过空间与时间交织出超现实主义，一场如梦般的旅程。Weberg描述影片为“艺术家的抽象非线性叙事摘要的运动图像”。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/culture/2016/04/141_202812.html|title=World's longest movie trailer: seven hours and 20 minutes|website=Korea Times|access-date=2016-04-19|archive-date=2016-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422194035/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/culture/2016/04/141_202812.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

截至2016年，Weberg声称已经完成了400小时的录像。为了在发行日期前完成电影，他必须每周拍摄7到8小时的录像。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/ambiance-720-hour-long-movie-by-anders-weberg-gets-short-seven-hour-trailer-1555519|title=Ambiance: 720-hour movie by Anders Weberg gets short 7-hour trailer|website=International Business Times UK|access-date=2016-04-19|archive-date=2016-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420103449/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/ambiance-720-hour-long-movie-by-anders-weberg-gets-short-seven-hour-trailer-1555519|dead-url=no}}</ref>Weberg已经为这部电影发行两部预告片，其中第一部在2014年发行，长达72分钟。他在2016年发布了第二部预告片，时长为439分钟（约7小时20分钟），并表示将在2018年发布一个72小时的预告片。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/ambianc-the-worlds-longest-ever-film-gets-a-seven-hour-trailer-a6989561.html|title=The world's longest ever film gets a seven hour trailer|website=The Independent|language=en-GB|access-date=2016-04-19|archive-date=2016-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160419012516/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/ambianc-the-worlds-longest-ever-film-gets-a-seven-hour-trailer-a6989561.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/trailers/news/a791015/this-movie-trailer-is-over-7-hours-long/|title=This movie trailer is over 7 hours long|date=2016-04-18|website=Digital Spy|access-date=2016-04-19|archive-date=2016-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420150239/http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/trailers/news/a791015/this-movie-trailer-is-over-7-hours-long/|dead-url=no}}</ref>第二个预告片采用了没有删减的单一录像<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/ambiance-trailer-longest-film-ever-made-30-days-20160417|title='Ambiancé' Trailer: Longest Film Ever Made (30 Days) Reveals Seven-Hour Teaser|last=Nordine|first=Michael|website=Indiewire|access-date=2016-04-19|archive-date=2016-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160418162944/http://www.indiewire.com/article/ambiance-trailer-longest-film-ever-made-30-days-20160417|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并于2016年7月20日从互联网上删除。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://time.com/2976242/watch-trailer-for-longest-movie/|title=Watch a 72-Minute Teaser for a Month-Long Movie, If You Dare|last=Rothman|first=Lily|website=TIME.com|access-date=2016-04-19|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306195605/http://time.com/2976242/watch-trailer-for-longest-movie/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

